textline.data: The system shall store pressure readings of
the sensor at a collision-protected Hard disc
The system shall turn on a LED in the cabin
at a pressure higher than 20 bar for 60 seconds
The system shall get readings from a preasure
sensor having ability to read pressure higher
than 20 bar and even higher values
The system shall detect if the pressure in the
cabin is higher than a predefined value = 20 bar
The system shall save Pressure readings
The system shall inform the crew in the cabin
that the pressure have reached a high value
The system shall protect the crew
The system shall detect high pressure
